# PRIVATE-MARKERS.list.example — copy to PRIVATE-MARKERS.list (gitignored) and fill in.
# One marker per line; '#' = comment. Case-insensitive substring match; the scan never
# echoes the marker text. Add your real personal markers: personal email(s), legal name,
# private codenames. Do NOT add your public handle or noreply email (public by design),
# and avoid short strings (e.g. 'ew') that match innocuous words like 'new'/'view'.
